descriptionHtml:
RaceMenu preset of my character, Katerina.

[size=4]REQUIRED MODS[/size]

Utilities (install in the order as listed):
[list]
[*][url=http://skse.silverlock.org/][size=2]SKSE[/size][/url]
[*][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/3863/?][size=2]SkyUI[/size][/url]
[*][size=2][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?]RaceMenu[/url][/size]
[*][size=2][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/33526/?]ShowRaceMenu Precache Killer[/url][/size]
[/list]Face/Hair:[list]
[*][size=2][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/68311/?]KS Hairdos[/url][/size]
[*][size=2][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/30411/?]Brows[/url][/size]
[*][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13722/?][size=2]The Eyes of Beauty[/size][/url]
[/list][size=2]Re-textures (optional, but provide best look):[/size][list]
[*][size=2][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/3563/?]Coverwomen[/url] (a good alternative is [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/2812/?]Better Females[/url])[/size]
[*][size=2][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35327/?]SG Female Eyebrows[/url][/size]
[/list]

[size=4]INSALLATION[/size]
[list=1]
[*]After downloading, place the file in Skyrim/Data/SKSE/Plugins/CharGen/Presets
[*]Launch the game using SKSE
[*]Load a game or start a new one (if you're starting a new game, skip ahead to step 6)
[*][size=2]Hit the tilde (~) button to open the console[/size]
[*][size=2]Type in "showracemenu" (without the quotes) and hit enter[/size]
[*][size=2]Select the Imperial race[/size]
[*][size=2]Go to the presets tab[/size]
[*][size=2]Press F9 and select the file "Katerina"[/size]
[*][size=2]Feel free to customize further[/size]
[/list]
author: LieutenantLeah
